(2030, 830, 'Lol :)  We gotta step up our base and perc on this song for sure!', 61, '2015-12-26 10:35:10'),
(2031, 804, 'Yah, the lyrics gave me chills - resonated with me to my core...', 61, '2015-12-26 11:02:59'),
