(2045, 865, 'I had a bit of trouble wrapping my mind around the line "we are free to struggle," so here''s a quick explanation from Tenth Avenue North about what it means: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NzJCsXdXBKk', 50, '2015-12-26 17:52:09'),
