(2049, 812, '@Hans YES. Sometimes I believe the lie that I''m alone in my struggle and fear and sorrow, but God is always with us and He will one day heal all the scars. We have so much joy in hope because we cling to God and we can look beyond this broken life to His coming kingdom.', 50, '2015-12-26 18:13:00'),
