(2230, 14, 'Oh yeah, I really like the way the solos were done on this one (not biased at all haha)', 62, '2016-05-28 20:50:21'),
(2231, 843, 'Definitely was one of my favorites at BIDB as well. The praise mixed with broken thankfulness is so raw and powerful in this song.', 64, '2016-05-28 20:51:50'),
(2232, 920, 'So good! I definitely agree with no solo and layering over the first verse. I think we could get a really great arrangement together.', 64, '2016-05-28 20:56:16'),
(2233, 876, 'Seems to fit our style pretty well, this could be a lot of fun, and I really like the message. Is the Xlinked thing a problem? I also like the fact that it''s pre-arranged.', 63, '2016-05-29 02:46:02'),
