(2252, 924, 'I agree, Matthew that this song would be very relatable. Depending on how many other slower songs we are looking at, I think this could be a good option for us :) ', 64, '2016-05-29 19:34:46'),
(2253, 881, 'You say that like we have to have exactly one hymn.\r\nHonestly this one sounds really cheesy to me. Might just be the recording, might just be the arrangement, but I''m not really compelled.', 62, '2016-05-29 19:34:50'),
(2254, 218, 'Yeah, this song tends to come off as cheesy to me. Maybe if it was done really well--and I think being a cappella helps--it could work.', 62, '2016-05-29 19:35:57'),
(2255, 462, 'The solo''s not like countertenor high, but it is consistently high, kind of like Mountains was. I''d prefer it to be a male solo. Depending on the arrangement, we could maybe take it down a step or two.', 62, '2016-05-29 19:37:41'),
(2256, 581, 'We already have an arrangement of it, but it was done Fall 2013 so we don''t have any good videos. Maybe somebody has the mixer recordings?', 62, '2016-05-29 19:40:12'),
