(2416, 983, '', 68, '2016-12-14 22:14:21'),
(2417, 986, 'This is one of my favorites from my home church :)  It''s our call to action of us knowing all the amazing things God has done for us!', 55, '2016-12-14 23:09:39'),
(2418, 986, 'Also, in my opinion, it''s better faster than in the video.', 55, '2016-12-14 23:11:30'),
(2419, 987, 'Yay another one of my favorite songs from my home church!  I love how upbeat it can get- everyone at church always loves singing along.  I think my favorite part of this song is the pre-chorus- the first two verses say "who was xxxx" but the last verse shows all the amazing things we can do with God (Phillippians 4:13 anyone??) and shows that we, through God, can do incredible things "who are justice for the poor, who are rage against the night, who are hope for peaceful people who are light"', 55, '2016-12-14 23:23:23'),
