(2453, 873, 'Still think this would be a great song to have edited specifically for MIT.', 58, '2016-12-18 04:21:35'),
(2454, 980, 'I think this is a cool song from God''s perceptive that he is always there for us ''when we''re lost'' and he won''t let us go.', 58, '2016-12-18 04:24:44'),
(2455, 810, 'I definitely think that it is possible to make an arrangement that is workable.  We managed to pull of Like A Match pretty well this year and I feel like we have more ''swag'' than we have in the past so I think it might be a good semester to try it.', 58, '2016-12-18 04:26:31'),
