(2469, 963, 'I really like this song!  I''ve never really thought of it as a Christian song, but I think it could work.  Maybe replace "baby" with an "ooooohhh" vocalization- I think it''d work cause there''s enough other "ooohhh" vocalizations in the song.', 55, '2016-12-18 04:59:04'),
(2470, 963, 'It might work musically, but it''s fairly well known, so I think people would notice.', 62, '2016-12-18 05:00:43'),
