(2486, 464, 'So pretty. I can see this becoming the "We Dance" of our Spring setlist.', 69, '2016-12-22 03:31:34'),
(2487, 745, 'Such a positive and uplifting song. Spring break friendly, too.', 69, '2016-12-22 03:42:37'),
(2488, 808, '^ Agree with previous comments. Solo slow, but marks potential for an interesting background arrangement.', 69, '2016-12-22 03:44:30'),
(2489, 973, 'Feel-good song about how the many ways God triumphs over our struggles.', 69, '2016-12-22 03:57:33'),
