(2491, 701, '^ Agree with previous comments. Really pretty song though.', 69, '2016-12-22 04:02:21'),
(2492, 865, 'Relatively spring break friendly. Love the message -- though agree with above comments. Very potent message when you understand what "we are free to struggle" means.', 69, '2016-12-22 04:05:05'),
(2493, 973, 'I do like the feel and the message of this one. I think it could be made really interesting on the musical side.', 64, '2016-12-22 04:05:53'),
